DATA;
/* GH #129 regression fixture. Wall #30 carries OwnerHistory #8; the
   pset rel #43 carries a DIFFERENT OwnerHistory #9 (referenced by
   nothing else) and attaches its psets through an INLINE IFC4
   IfcPropertySetDefinitionSet aggregate (#40,#45) rather than a bare
   ref. Subsetting wall #30 retains rel #43 verbatim — so #9, #40 and
   #45 must be forward-closed with it or the output dangles. */
